TASK 5 – Firewall Configuration

Installed UFW:
sudo apt update
sudo apt install ufw -y

Set default policies:
sudo ufw default deny incoming
sudo ufw default allow outgoing

Allowed required ports:
sudo ufw allow 22
sudo ufw allow 80
sudo ufw allow 8000

Enabled firewall:
sudo ufw enable

Checked status:
sudo ufw status verbose

Verified SSH:
ssh anil@localhost

Verified web application:
http://localhost:8000

Result:
Firewall configured successfully allowing only required ports.
